Package: growlight
Priority: standard
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends} 
Recommends: dosfstools, zfs, jfsutils, xfsprogs, mdadm, dmsetup, ntfs-3g, btrfs-tools
Description: Disk manipulation and system preparation tool
 Growlight can manipulate both real and virtual (mdadm, device-mapper, and
 ZFS) disks, find bottlenecks in a storage setup, create partitions and
 filesystems, and prepare fstab files for new installations.

Package: growlight-udeb
Section: debian-installer
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, hw-detect, md-modules, mdadm-udeb, dmsetup-udeb, libpci3-udeb, libcryptsetup4-udeb, libatasmart4-udeb, libpciaccess0-udeb, kbd-udeb, e2fsprogs-udeb, zfs-udeb, dosfstools-udeb, jfsutils-udeb, xfsprogs-udeb, ntfs-3g-udeb, btrfs-tools-udeb
Replaces: partman, partitioner, grub-installer, lilo-installer
Provides: bootable-system, harddrive-detection, partitioned-harddrives, made-filesystems, made-swapspace, mounted-partitions, created-fstab
Breaks: grub-installer, lilo-installer
XB-Installer-Menu-Item: 4200
XC-Package-Type: udeb
Description: Prepare target
 Growlight udeb, unsuitable for installation on normal machines.
